{"tid":337990,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅的歌陪住長大","createTime":"2017-07-27T18:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T22:54:59.000Z","uid":14730,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5514b5aacb6369dd8b6d403bd600cef947cca3","tid":337990,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:55:21.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅43歲生日快樂！回看Eason 在樂壇打滾了那麼多年，眾多的Eason金曲總會有一首是你心底的寫照，每人也有一首「陳奕迅」代表心聲。<br />\n<br />\n最正都係呢首， 《陀飛輪》。<br />\n<br />\n「用我尚有換我沒有，其實已用盡所擁有」<br />\n出來社會工作了幾年，心力付出了，從前買不到的玩意，名錶、跑車、相機、美酒都一一到手，可是心靈呢？這一刻看到眼前的一切只不過如霧似水，過眼雲煙，原來這些年來的自己並不「富有」，因為自己工作上的努力只能換來物質上數字上的富有，卻一直違背自己意願。作為社會成功人士的你，為工作努力了十多年開始迷失的你，看到這些歌詞應該別有一番感覺吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2u2kbAp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2u2kbAp&d=5f8aTq4Pbr%2B9gATaFqyk6C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d3a2bb0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2u2kbAp</a>"},{"pid":"b3b055cc7c649d5fe215e03176e3753bea6c95a3","tid":337990,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T20:19:30.000Z","msg":"時光倒流二十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fbde3c25c3953f4bc724f84fa4800435e4b4e7","tid":337990,"uid":124708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:27:48.000Z","msg":"我 想好好抉擇 好想嗌暫停想一想哪樣過<br />\n怕 想一想以後 身邊觀眾便離座<br />\n<br />\n始終敵不過時間<br />\n以前就不斷讀讀讀<br />\n而家就不斷做做做<br />\n搵得少少錢 冇左好多時間<br />\n而且身邊既朋友越嚟越少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c30a0d83b13c2084954bf6ef16091819a131adf","tid":337990,"uid":99364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:50:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f74bc4761ab05f5a0a47e5ea0476d0d5f1732a92","tid":337990,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係 我有粒兄弟都好鍾意陳奕迅 不過佢死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e0bd2e6b2b65d779a41d50e88ecddf022c8ece","tid":337990,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:54:59.000Z","msg":"當潮流愛新鮮"}]}